OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPerhaps some
OL,6,Fearly evening bright or sunny spells,
OL,7,Fmainly in the southeast, but cloud
OL,8,Fsoon thickening. Then mostly cloudy
OL,9,Fwith outbreaks of rain spreading east,
OL,10,Fthese occasionally heavy. Turning a
OL,11,Flittle breezy, but mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FA mostly cloudy start with
OL,14,Fshowers for many. Sunny spells
OL,15,Fgradually developing, with showers
OL,16,Fbecoming confined to the Pennines
OL,17,Fbefore dying out completely later.
OL,18,FBreezy, and cooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
